{"tid":1826550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CCTVB:訂購的廣告只會於myTV SUPER平台中出現，唔需要擔心因廣告出現於不適當環境而帶來的品牌安全問題。","createTime":"2020-01-16T08:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T05:39:54.000Z","uid":171506,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"02b286db4078be3e44f27d53d5e8ad9163a7aff8","tid":1826550,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T08:36:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1642241389355834/posts/2623198931260070/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1642241389355834%2Fposts%2F2623198931260070%2F&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GObr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=9e7e6cb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1642241389355834/posts/2623198931260070/</a><br />\n<br />\n忽然睇到呢個CCTVB旗下myTV SUPER嘅自助落廣告計劃！（出個新Post，等大家Share唔會得佢條Link)<br />\n<br />\n其中佢有一句好正：ABM訂購的廣告只會於myTV SUPER平台中出現，唔需要擔心因廣告出現於不適當環境而帶來的品牌安全問題。<br />\n<br />\nCCTVB已經去到崩潰狀況啦，自己都講到明喺電視平台落廣告，可能會有人狙擊啲品牌呀！<br />\n<br />\n大家嘅清算係有效架！加油呀<br />\n<br />\n廣告清算師係咪要Mon埋myTV  SUPER 呀？<br />\n<br />\n佢地條LINK<br />\n<a href=\"https://adbooking.mytvsuper.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fadbooking.mytvsuper.com%2F&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GObr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=06bb9359\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://adbooking.mytvsuper.com/</a>"},{"pid":"44dce17eb7128e1a17b0c45e8506422d4c5222d7","tid":1826550,"uid":202464,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T08:38:39.000Z","msg":"mytvsuper咪一樣不適當環境。"},{"pid":"b43f1f0090d63af1dae387160268f0912eb19f6b","tid":1826550,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T08:38:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d51be767a0428ef16f7ed430bc89cd7f4ed37ce0","tid":1826550,"uid":2772,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T08:40:12.000Z","msg":"TVB=不適當環境<br />\n鬼拍後尾枕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma